<br>
<br>
1. Mask scent.<br>
<br>
2. Walk to the baby, making sure to stay behind the most dangerous critters in the area that may notice you. (It seems to me that if you are walking behind a creature that your chance of being smelled is lower... but I can't confirm that with empirical data.)<br>
<br>
3. Then, when you are about 20m from the baby, go prone and /follow it... hitting /tame at the 10 meter mark.<br>
<br>
4. If the first attempt fails, and the baby does not attack, you should have just enough time to try once more before you have to leave. (walk as you leave, don't run)<br>
<br>
5. Unmask and Remask scent and try again.<br>
<br>
<br>
Note:<br>
<br>
If a non-deathblow baby attacks you and other mobs assist it, you can try to get to a relatively safe spot between lairs before you allow it(them) to incapacitate you.<br>
<br>
If the babies parents will deathblow, use burstrun as you spam peace and get to a safe distance away. Then, wait a few minutes (I wait 5 minutes just as a rule of thumb) to make sure you're forgotten before remasking and trying again. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub60.ezboard.com/fcreaturehandlersofswgfrm7.showPrevMessage?topicID=12.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub60.ezboard.com/fcreaturehandlersofswgfrm7.showNextMessage?topicID=12.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub60.ezboard.com/fcreaturehandlersofswgfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=12.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/black_default/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub60.ezboard.com/fcreaturehandlersofswgfrm7.emailToFriend?topicID=12.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub60.ezboard.com/fcreaturehandlersofswgfrm7.threadControl?topicID=12.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/black_default/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub60.ezboard.com/fcreaturehandlersofswgfrm7.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=12.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub60.ezboard.com/fcreaturehandlersofswgfrm7.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=12.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop rece